{"tid":628883,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"網店/樓上鋪/零售/創業 廣告宣傳交流","createTime":"2018-04-14T09:07:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T10:07:46.000Z","uid":110749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7f8edfa34d3b85c73311e39e8a341c92d07e7c4a","tid":628883,"uid":110749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T09:07:10.000Z","msg":"有無人做緊同類野？？我一月開始做網店<br />\n整左個網頁 可以自已自助比錢 落單<br />\n開左個FACEBOOK PAGE 同 IG<br />\n<br />\n一開始唔係好我識FACEBOOK落廣告，倒左好多錢落去都無乜成效<br />\n大部份錢去不停試，儲左千零個LIKE<br />\n但發覺FACEBOOK PAGE，一唔比錢做廣告<br />\n出個新POST，得一百 幾十人接觸到，勁少互動，好難做<br />\n<br />\n之後轉左IG試下，而家儲左三千幾FOLLOW<br />\n落廣告無得好似FACEBOOK咁多SETTING<br />\n出POST多左人LIKE～多左人問價，但大多數都係齋LIKE唔買<br />\n不過IG感覺上無FACEBOOK PAGE咁仆街<br />\n唔比錢就睇唔到你個POST<br />\n<br />\n錢就賺得唔多，大半都貢獻哂落去做廣告<br />\n每個月 平均月都有幾千蚊落袋 做零用錢<br />\n玩左幾個月，覺得真係好難做得好<br />\n落廣告又無一個準則，無人話比你聽做得正唔正確<br />\n有時落成千蚊 都無單返，有時又無啦啦 突然勁好生意<br />\n真係做到R哂頭<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/170547_766fa9df6ba3dc25d27e4a61cde86883.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F170547_766fa9df6ba3dc25d27e4a61cde86883.png&h=f45e2832&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/170548_e87e69252bdfa609a8051a912e9edd1b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F170548_e87e69252bdfa609a8051a912e9edd1b.png&h=af8afb47&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/170549_940d1630cbdba9b25328f81096f74aa9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F170549_940d1630cbdba9b25328f81096f74aa9.png&h=5ede453e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1dc201720b3d847593f9885f16d065104a0ed6f0","tid":628883,"uid":38071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T09:10:52.000Z","msg":"唔好淨係靠interest嗰啲demographic嚟做target <br />\n有無自己儲audience list去做remarketing呀？"},{"pid":"78bc9525aba2c40cddf9632f3ae7c7e677be91b1","tid":628883,"uid":110749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dc201720b3d847593f9885f16d065104a0ed6f0","tid":628883,"uid":38071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T09:10:52.000Z","msg":"唔好淨係靠interest嗰啲demographic嚟做target <br />\n有無自己儲audience list去做remarketing呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T09:17:09.000Z","msg":"無呀，要點做？指教下？"},{"pid":"18d34127e4058bf4ff859912d5286fcc87e09e6f","tid":628883,"uid":56180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T09:21:25.000Z","msg":"留明"},{"pid":"82aa65984600624b06077a69b039c601a3dae2d8","tid":628883,"uid":2882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T09:25:39.000Z","msg":"網店賣咩？<br />\n最近都有興趣做下網店 但發現香港真係冇一個好D既平台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"881c5149b758de9d1a671cd6d643a0c636883950","tid":628883,"uid":110749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82aa65984600624b06077a69b039c601a3dae2d8","tid":628883,"uid":2882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T09:25:39.000Z","msg":"網店賣咩？<br />\n最近都有興趣做下網店 但發現香港真係冇一個好D既平台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T09:35:26.000Z","msg":"賣男仔衫 同d男士用品"},{"pid":"e842dee2cf5c9723502bcbf0474353da07e4bdf2","tid":628883,"uid":38071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T09:37:13.000Z","msg":"你可以target返去過你個網度嘅人甚至買過嘢嘅人或者擺咗貨喺shopping cart嘅人。擺個facebook gen出嚟嘅tracking code（正式嘅名叫pixel）去你個網相應嘅page度，例如target買過嘢嘅客咪擺個code落thank you page，然後facebook就可以track到佢地。<br />\n或者如果你有啲客嘅email就可以直接俾啲email facebook去target。<br />\n<br />\n不過視乎你賣啲咩啦。如果你係ztore嗰啲賣嘢食日用品嘅鋪頭就值得retarget買過嘢嘅人，因為佢地買得密。如果係賣手作嘢，感覺無買得咁密<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁樣retarget上過你個網嘅人就有用啲啦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.socialmediaexaminer.com/how-to-refine-facebook-audience-for-better-ad-targeting/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.socialmediaexaminer.com%2Fhow-to-refine-facebook-audience-for-better-ad-targeting%2F&d=as0WiOeuhvz8opnM8qFyT54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=12656381\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.socialmediaexaminer.com/how-to-refine-facebook-audience-for-better-ad-targeting/</a>"},{"pid":"b885433226a3122c6df4a2ae22f9de11077d6a19","tid":628883,"uid":66254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T09:43:22.000Z","msg":"個po應該改名做Digital交流區"},{"pid":"3444ddea7f84e3a5df25b5bbe0e16e970c8c560f","tid":628883,"uid":38071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T09:54:03.000Z","msg":"btw，視乎你個feed嘅content較返對同一個人show嘅次數，可以慳錢又可以避免煩親啲客。<br />\n有時啲page出埋啲on9 post都要係咁show俾我睇，睇到都覺得曬錢。"},{"pid":"676fe6e5798e4a2a6718bd46bcb9212ab1fd994e","tid":628883,"uid":110749,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e842dee2cf5c9723502bcbf0474353da07e4bdf2","tid":628883,"uid":38071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T09:37:13.000Z","msg":"你可以target返去過你個網度嘅人甚至買過嘢嘅人或者擺咗貨喺shopping cart嘅人。擺個facebook gen出嚟嘅tracking code（正式嘅名叫pixel）去你個網相應嘅page度，例如target買過嘢嘅客咪擺個code落thank you page，然後facebook就可以track到佢地。<br />\n或者如果你有啲客嘅email就可以直接俾啲email facebook去target。<br />\n<br />\n不過視乎你賣啲咩啦。如果你係ztore嗰啲賣嘢食日用品嘅鋪頭就值得retarget買過嘢嘅人，因為佢地買得密。如果係賣手作嘢，感覺無買得咁密<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁樣retarget上過你個網嘅人就有用啲啦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.socialmediaexaminer.com/how-to-refine-facebook-audience-for-better-ad-targeting/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.socialmediaexaminer.com%2Fhow-to-refine-facebook-audience-for-better-ad-targeting%2F&d=as0WiOeuhvz8opnM8qFyT54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=12656381\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.socialmediaexaminer.com/how-to-refine-facebook-audience-for-better-ad-targeting/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T10:07:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/180715_8754a8c336d8070dd42a9efefab4d14e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F180715_8754a8c336d8070dd42a9efefab4d14e.png&h=d1e0f13f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用邊個黎做，會比較好<br />\n玩左咁耐，我都唔係好識分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}